OL,2,MWhy is the hacker scene so damn queer?
OL,4,CGero "zweifeln" Nagel
OL,5,CFri 12:30-13:00
OL,6,CStage A
OL,8,GAt the first glance sexuality doesn't
OL,9,Ghave much to do with technology. But
OL,10,Gunderstanding the history and
OL,11,Ginterlinking between both fields is
OL,12,Ghelpful to understand both scenes
OL,13,Gbetter. As everything involving
OL,14,Ghumans, things are a bit blurry, terms
OL,15,Gand concepts change and with these
OL,16,Galso the understanding. In philosophy
OL,17,Gthere is a concept "hermeneutical
OL,18,Gcircle" which means, you go around a
OL,19,Gsubject from different perspectives
OL,20,Gand often end up where you started but
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
